snippet.title: National Park Girls - Episode 2: Happy Trails Trailer
snippet.description:
National Park Girls - Episode 2: Happy Trails is the second installment in the episodic visual novel National Park Girls. Join Eve as she goes on a (reluctant) hike with Yellowstone, learns more about the girls' origins, and causes the end of western civilization!

Coming October, 21st!
